warning_description: Serious side effects seen with these medicines. These included confusion and loss of consciousness, particularly in elderly people, and the risk of addiction to the medicine when used for prolonged periods, with severe withdrawal symptoms on stopping treatment abruptly. The French medicines agency was also concerned by reports of these medicines being taken for longer than recommended and cases of overdose (sometimes in combination with other medicines) leading to coma or death.
